OL,3,CInquest into death of baby hears he
OL,4,Cwas given 10 times his medical dose
OL,6,FAn inquest into the death of a six-
OL,7,Fmonth-old boy hears how he was given
OL,8,Ften times the dose of medication
OL,9,Fleading up to his death at Royal
OL,10,FHospital.
OL,12,FHunter Martin was admitted to hospital
OL,13,Fwith suspected chicken pox on March
OL,14,F4th last year.
OL,16,FDespite the concerns of his parents
OL,17,FJade Smith and Alex Martin, he was
OL,18,Fgiven ibuprofen and sent home.
