OL,3,CInquest into death of baby hears he
OL,4,Cwas given 10 times his medical dose
OL,6,FBut overnight, Hunter's condition
OL,7,Fworsened and he was rushed back to
OL,8,Fhospital and to a high-dependency ward.
OL,10,FHe was then diagnosed with sepsis and
OL,11,Finvasive group A streptococcal
OL,12,Fdisease. Hunter was then administered
OL,13,Fthe antibiotic drug Clindamycin.
OL,15,FHe should have been given 94
OL,16,Fmilligrams of the drug. However,
OL,17,Fmedics at the hospital gave the infant
OL,18,F940 milligrams - 10 times the
OL,19,Frecommended dose.
