OL,3,CInquest into death of baby hears he
OL,4,Cwas given 10 times his medical dose
OL,6,FA jury at the inquest at
OL,7,FChesterfield's Coroners Court today
OL,8,F(June 3) heard, Hunter was later
OL,9,Ftransferred to Sheffield Children's
OL,10,FHospital, but he died later that day
OL,11,Fafter suffering three cardiac arrests.
OL,13,FAt the hearing, a statement from
OL,14,FHunter's mother Jade was read out, in
OL,15,Fwhich she described her son as "a
OL,16,Fbonnie blue-eyed angel".
OL,18,FShe also spoke of how when she'd taken
OL,19,FHunter to the hospital the second
OL,20,Ftime, she'd told staff his body was
OL,21,Fswollen and his eyes were puffy.
