OL,3,CInquest into death of baby hears he
OL,4,Cwas given 10 times his medical dose
OL,6,FBut they were told that was probably
OL,7,Fjust excess fluid. As well, when
OL,8,FHunter was gasping and retching it was
OL,9,Fbecause he had an empty stomach.
OL,11,FJade's statement ended with her
OL,12,Fsaying: "We miss Hunter terribly and
OL,13,Fthere is a deathly silence that
OL,14,Flingers over our lives now."
