OL,3,CInquest into death of baby hears he
OL,4,Cwas given 10 times his medical dose
OL,6,FThe inquest today heard from two
OL,7,Fmedical experts, toxicologist
OL,8,FStephaine Martin who told the jury
OL,9,Fthat the possible effects of excess
OL,10,Fclindamycin included acute kidney
OL,11,Finjury but also neuro-muscular
OL,12,Fparalysis, resulting in the drop of
OL,13,Fthe breathing rate.
OL,15,FPathologist Nadia Burgess was asked if
OL,16,Fexcess clindamycin could've
OL,17,Fcontributed to the death.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
