OL,3,CInquest into death of baby hears he
OL,4,Cwas given 10 times his medical dose
OL,6,FShe replied: "There is compelling
OL,7,Fevidence for infection being the main
OL,8,Fcause of death but I can't totally
OL,9,Fdisregard the potential part
OL,10,Fclindamycin played in this process."
OL,12,FThe Trust which runs Chesterfield
OL,13,FRoyal Hospital has admitted there were
OL,14,Fmissed opportunities to diagnose
OL,15,FHunter and had Hunter been given the
OL,16,Fcorrect antibiotics earlier, on the
OL,17,Fbalance of probabilities he might have
OL,18,Fsurvived.
