OL,3,CInquest into death of baby hears he
OL,4,Cwas given 10 times his medical dose
OL,6,FThey also admitted there had been an
OL,7,Ferror in the dosage of antibiotics
OL,8,Fgiven to Hunter but they are not clear
OL,9,Fwhether this contributed to Hunter's
OL,10,Fdeterioration.
OL,12,FThe inquest is expected to conclude
OL,13,Fearly next week.
